+        └── segment_router.py
+```
+
+### Existing Modules (Unchanged)
+```
+chromadb/
+├── db/                        # Database layer
+├── segment/                   # Segment implementations
+├── ingest/                    # Event streaming
+├── auth/                      # Authentication
+├── server/                    # Server implementations
+├── telemetry/                 # Telemetry clients
